Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever even think that the guy might be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,ME?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... even if it's just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him to think of me as a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:03.24,Title,,200,0,85,,Comeback Impossible! Major Heartbreak!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:03.24,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...I want him to think about me in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's thinking hard. He's thinking hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's definitely realized this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Risa. Your hard work has paid off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I did something completely unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to do anything. You did everything you had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's all down to Otani-kun's reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,His reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better go tell him I was just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he's an idiot! I like that idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'll be in the way, but let me hang out with you on the class trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine by me, but what about Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't spoken to him at all since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we finally have our class trip too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! I don't care about the class trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered there's something I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go with whatever you think is best, just tell her what you're thinking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm thinking now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted him to think about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...but if I stop being All-Kyojin, then what will I become?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I really become a normal girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you ever think that the guy might be you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After going around in a big circle, I finally told Otani how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is going to happen to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so preoccupied with telling him how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I never even thought about what would come after.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's all down to Otani-kun's reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,His reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, Koizumi, I've liked you all this time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. That's absolutely impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared! I bet he's gonna say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll definitely say something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I'll just avoid being alone with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine as long as I don't speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How long have I slept in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Good morning. Koizumi speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Good morning"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You just woke up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot we've got our class trip today, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been calling you for ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The bus to the airport is about to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,L... Late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,S- S- Sorry! I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't there anyone to wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else at home was asleep as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking the two of you, don't pull a comedy act at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"The two of you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm la—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning on not being alone with Otani for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh. We're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go take care of the tickets. You guys just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pair of idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Th- This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave us alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I said sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to act natural. Just like I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you sleep in on such an important day, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You did too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W- W- W- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be blunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't said anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! Don't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been calling me an idiot for so long it's really starting to piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the guy you like really me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking so directly is bad for my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any other way to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't, that I know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, and answer me properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I tried so hard to confess, you brushed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to make me relive that scene now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If saying sorry were enough, there'd be no need for cops in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to say it earlier, but you kept trickling away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "trickling away"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me sound like a shishiotoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize that you haven't heard a thing I've said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have said it in a way that's easier to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... like you, Otani!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I said in very simple terms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I came right out and told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're the one that wanted me to think in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...but hearing you say that so seriously really scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here, All Hanshin-Kyojin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised. Are you regretting being late?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Y- Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The late couple have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you? I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were together till morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, I was worr—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this! I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask the seagull, "Have the herring come?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm just a migrating bird. Ask the waves."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:46.24,Overlap,,0,0,0,,The plane trip was so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Otani sat right next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hard to breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you're being overly self-conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to think of a way to dump him five seconds before he dumps me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumps?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know if he's going to reject you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I do know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get your hopes up about ever finding a boyfriend, amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we All Hanshin-Kyojin partners?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What? I... I don't get you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To Otani, I'm just an amazon... and a comedy partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought that I might like him never even crossed his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I did confess, it'll never lead anywhere with someone who thinks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that you've told him, you're not a part of All Hanshin-Kyojin anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So at the very least, you've escaped from being his comedy partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great! You've worked hard and taken another step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Nobu-chan, what'll happen to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That depends on Otani-kun's  reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san sure is agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you slept so much that it made you late?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been getting enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that because you've been thinking about Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. Don't make me hit you, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone this scary can't be Otani... sniff, sniff, sniff...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, you're free to explore this area, but remember to meet back here at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, the late couple isn't waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake those idiots up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But they didn't even wake up when we stuffed snacks in their mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with those two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess there's not much we can do. Call them by cell phone and meet up with them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, I can't go out with a giant like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going out with this crab from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a Hokkaido specialty. She was just caught today, and is still fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Otani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh... Mongolian Lamb sounds good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why has it turned out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Glass? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. We're at the Otaru Canal Craft Hall—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? I have no idea what you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So we just follow the Otaru canal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Nobu-chan say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She said they'll get here soon, so we should run into them if we just wait around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean I took a step forward? This is definitely a step backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew it was going to be like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd rather keep things the way they were, just saying whatever we felt like saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that awkward topic is all I can think of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did... Did I fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn't have told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How awesome does that look?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rickshaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool! It totally suits the atmosphere here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna ride it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be embarrassing and touristy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go buy some souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how they're doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Risa and Otani are all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiharu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The rickshaw was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That felt great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It was super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The driver even gave us nicknames.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "How about I call you guys 'Suke-san' and 'Kaku-san'?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"You can bring Komon-san along next time."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a cold joke, but it was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna ride again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But we just did the 10 minute course. Should we go for the 30 minute course?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot. If we do that, we won't have any money for souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can just make some cash by doing a comedy act here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that things are finally going well between the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten all about that awkward feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go get some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys decide where to go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn't have confessed after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've probably been better if I'd forgotten this crush and we'd just stayed a comedy duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew it would be this awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd rather things had stayed the way they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-kun sure is slow. He still hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's deep in thought again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep in thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do you want to go shopping around here for a bit, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do, Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hurry, I can still make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell him to just pretend that nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If we pretend that nothing happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...then, just like before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the bear curry that a friend asked me to get, so I was going to buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.64,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Bear Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear... curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just pretend that nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... like you, Otani!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you ever even think that the guy might be you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing had happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked me to think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I've been thinking about it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're asking me whether I like you or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd say I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one I can make a big fuss and get excited about riding a rickshaw with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've been a comedy duo for such a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can suddenly see you as my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that serious expression?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sickening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sickening, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine. Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just pretend that nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually came to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just stay All Hanshin-Kyojin from now on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, maybe we can join a comedy troupe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, hurry up and buy your bear curry or seal curry or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, go on. Everyone is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go catch up with the others, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew from the start that it wouldn't go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even my confession was just to get him to see me as a girl for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Otani is... bear curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani is bear curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, what's this about bear curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, having it said to my face... it still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:20:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about the bear! What happened with Otani-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what are you? The spokesperson for bear curry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason I feel like having bear curry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, please don't speak right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi Risa, heartbroken!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, what do you want to do during our free time in Hakodate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get a soft serve!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Umibouzu, in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: Back from the dead!! Aim for girlfriend status!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
